media:group.media:description:
Stand out in the creative community with your photography skills. We’re challenging you with the shoot theme: Summer Moments. 

The winner chosen will receive a $250 gift card to Moment brand products [https://www.shopmoment.com/moment]

Upload submissions to your Dissolve Creators™ profile. Don't have a profile yet? Signing up is free and easy: https://dissolve.com/community

All contest details can be found here: https://dissolve.com/creators/challenges
